---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'healthcare-system', text: 'Healthcare System', level: 2 },
  { id: 'visa-requirements', text: 'Visa Options', level: 2 },
  { id: 'insurance-requirements', text: 'Insurance Requirements', level: 2 },
  { id: 'recommended-providers', text: 'Recommended Providers', level: 2 },
  { id: 'costs', text: 'Expected Costs', level: 2 },
  { id: 'scenarios', text: 'Real-World Scenarios', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'Common Questions', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Vanuatu Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/vanuatu/insurance' },
  { title: 'Insurance for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors' },
  { title: 'Fiji for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/fiji' },
  { title: 'Australia for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/australia' },
  { title: 'New Zealand for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/new-zealand' },
];

const providerColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'entryAge', header: 'Max Entry Age' },
  { key: 'renewal', header: 'Renewal' },
  { key: 'monthlyFrom', header: 'From (65-69)' },
  { key: 'vanuatuFit', header: 'Vanuatu Fit' },
];

const providerRows = [
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'VUV$53,100-75,860/mo', vanuatuFit: 'Excellent' },
  { provider: 'BUPA Global', entryAge: '79', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'VUV$62,100-88,700/mo', vanuatuFit: 'Excellent' },
  { provider: 'Allianz Care', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'VUV$47,790-68,275/mo', vanuatuFit: 'Very Good' },
  { provider: 'Now Health', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'VUV$44,400-63,430/mo', vanuatuFit: 'Very Good' },
];

const costColumns = [
  { key: 'category', header: 'Expense' },
  { key: 'monthly', header: 'Monthly' },
  { key: 'annual', header: 'Annual' },
];

const costRows = [
  { category: 'International Insurance (65-69)', monthly: 'VUV$47,790-75,860', annual: 'VUV$573K-910K' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (70-74)', monthly: 'VUV$65,545-101,150', annual: 'VUV$786K-1.21M' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (75-79)', monthly: 'VUV$88,060-135,710', annual: 'VUV$1.06M-1.63M' },
  { category: 'Private Clinic Visit', monthly: 'VUV$5,000-15,000/visit', annual: 'Affordable' },
  { category: 'Evacuation to Australia', monthly: 'N/A', annual: 'VUV$3.5M-10M' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Health Insurance for Seniors in Vanuatu 2026 | Retirement Guide"
  description="Guide to health insurance for seniors in Vanuatu. Volcano adventures, Melanesian culture, tax haven, and coverage for adventurous retirees 65+."
  headline="Health Insurance for Seniors in Vanuatu"
  subheadline="Vanuatu offers active volcanoes, Melanesian culture, tax-free living, pristine diving, and citizenship by investment—a Pacific adventure destination attracting those seeking tax efficiency and tropical lifestyle."
  heroImage="/images/countries/vanuatu-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Senior Plans →"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/cigna-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Why Seniors Choose Vanuatu</h2>
  <p>
    Vanuatu offers unique combination of active volcano experiences (Mount Yasur), Melanesian kastom culture, no income tax, world-class diving, and citizenship by investment. Popular with Australians and tax-conscious retirees. More adventurous than Fiji, more remote than most Pacific destinations.
  </p>

  <p>
    Port Vila (Efate) is capital with most services. Luganville (Espiritu Santo) has WWII history and diving. Tanna has Mount Yasur volcano. Population ~310,000. Brisbane is 3 hours flight; Auckland 3.5 hours—both provide medical backup.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Key Facts for Seniors</h3>
    <ul class="text-primary-800 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Limited; Australia/NZ evacuation common</li>
      <li><strong>Language:</strong> Bislama, English, French</li>
      <li><strong>Cost of Living:</strong> VUV$250,000-500,000/month (~$2,100-4,200 USD); moderate</li>
      <li><strong>Climate:</strong> Tropical; warm year-round; cyclone season</li>
      <li><strong>Character:</strong> Adventure; volcanic; laid-back</li>
      <li><strong>Tax:</strong> No income, capital gains, or inheritance tax</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="healthcare-system">Vanuatu Healthcare System</h2>
  <p>
    Vanuatu healthcare is limited—Vila Central Hospital is main public facility. ProMedical private clinic in Port Vila provides better care but limited specialists. Outer islands have basic health centers. Complex cases require evacuation to Brisbane (3 hours) or Auckland (3.5 hours).
  </p>

  <p>
    Brisbane provides closest quality backup—excellent hospitals just 3 hours away. International insurance with Australia evacuation coverage essential.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-2">Australia Evacuation Essential</h3>
    <p class="text-amber-800 mb-0">
      Brisbane is 3 hours away with Australian healthcare standards. Vanuatu cannot treat most complex conditions. Volcanic and cyclone activity adds risk. Insurance with Australia/NZ coverage is non-negotiable.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="visa-requirements">Visa Options for Seniors</h2>
  <p>
    Vanuatu visa options:
  </p>

  <h3>Visa Exemption</h3>
  <p>
    30 days visa-free for many nationalities. Simple entry.
  </p>

  <h3>Extended Visa</h3>
  <p>
    Extensions available through Immigration for longer stays.
  </p>

  <h3>Residence Permit</h3>
  <p>
    Various categories available. Investment options exist.
  </p>

  <h3>Citizenship by Investment</h3>
  <p>
    Development Support Program—$130,000+ for citizenship. Vanuatu passport provides visa-free access to 95+ countries including Schengen.
  </p>

  <h2 id="insurance-requirements">Insurance Requirements</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance requirements for Vanuatu:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Entry:</strong> Travel insurance strongly recommended</li>
    <li><strong>Extended stay:</strong> International coverage essential</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation:</strong> Australia/NZ coverage critical</li>
    <li><strong>Natural disasters:</strong> Volcanic and cyclone coverage</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Insurance Strategy for Vanuatu</h3>
    <p class="text-blue-800 mb-0">
      Comprehensive international insurance with strong Australia/NZ evacuation essential. Local care handles routine needs only. Include natural disaster coverage given volcanic activity and cyclone risk.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="recommended-providers">Recommended Insurance Providers</h2>
  <p>
    For seniors in Vanuatu, regional evacuation coverage critical:
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={providerColumns} rows={providerRows} />

  <h3>Why These Providers Work for Vanuatu</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cigna Global:</strong> Strong Pacific/Australia network</li>
    <li><strong>BUPA Global:</strong> Highest entry age (79), comprehensive</li>
    <li><strong>Australia access:</strong> Brisbane 3 hours away</li>
    <li><strong>Natural disaster:</strong> Volcanic/cyclone coverage</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Get Personalized Senior Quotes</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Compare coverage for Vanuatu with Australia evacuation.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
      <a href="/go/bupa-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get BUPA Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="costs">Expected Insurance Costs</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance costs for Vanuatu (VUV ~118 to USD):
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

  <h3>Cost Considerations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Tax-free:</strong> No income tax offsets living costs</li>
    <li><strong>Australia proximity:</strong> Quick evacuation access</li>
    <li><strong>Moderate costs:</strong> Higher than Fiji, lower than Australia</li>
    <li><strong>CBI option:</strong> Citizenship program available</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="scenarios">Real-World Scenarios</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 1: Australian Escapee, 67</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> AUD$4,000/month. Tax optimization. Port Vila.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Cigna Global with Australia coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~VUV$55,000/month (~$465). Tax-free; Brisbane backup close.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 2: Diving Enthusiast, 66</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $3,500/month. Espiritu Santo. WWII wrecks.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> BUPA Global with diving coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~VUV$65,000/month (~$550). World-class diving; comprehensive backup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 3: CBI Citizen, 69</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $5,000/month. Citizenship by investment. Global traveler.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Allianz Care worldwide coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~VUV$50,000/month (~$425). Passport benefits; global coverage.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="faqs">Common Questions</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is the volcano dangerous?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Mount Yasur (Tanna) is one of world's most accessible active volcanoes—tourists visit crater rim. Volcanic alerts occasionally issued. Other islands less affected. Adds adventure appeal. Monitor volcano status.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What's the citizenship program?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Development Support Program—$130,000+ donation for Vanuatu citizenship. Passport provides Schengen visa-free access. No residency requirement. Popular with those seeking second passport.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What about cyclones?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Real risk—Cyclone Pam (2015) was devastating. Season November-April. Proper construction matters. Insurance should cover weather evacuation. Less risky than some Pacific locations but prepare.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Why Vanuatu over Fiji?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Tax-free (Fiji has income tax), more adventurous (volcanoes), CBI available, unique Melanesian culture. Fiji has better infrastructure and healthcare. Vanuatu for tax and adventure; Fiji for ease.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Ready to Compare Options?</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Get quotes from providers for Vanuatu coverage.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
      <a href="/go/allianz-care" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Allianz Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-0">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide is for informational purposes only. Vanuatu has active volcanoes and cyclone risk. Healthcare limited—Australia evacuation essential. Always verify current conditions and requirements.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
